name: Union Suits
description:
This is a LoRA model trained on 512x512 images of men wearing union suits a.k.a onesies, one-piece long johns, thermal underwear.

Example prompt: "a man wearing a union suit" + Lora tag. CFG ~3.5

You may need to dial down the weight to as low as 0.3 or 0.4 to get different body types and locations.

Have fun and share your results and feedback below.
